Otherwise, the chosen Class will be used to determine the Affects Class effect. ANY CLASS - Players with a Class assigned, regardless of what Class it is. NO CLASS - Players without any assigned class.

UserOptionDefinition.Device_ArmoredBattleBusSpawner_V2_C.Star: The percentage of fuel in the vehicle's fuel tank at spawn.
